02:18.710 --> 02:21.575
These guys came here unarmed, right?
That was the deal.

02:22.192 --> 02:24.270
Still, whoever did this
took them out pretty quickly,

02:24.295 --> 02:25.539
or else we could've stopped them.

02:25.540 --> 02:26.855
No, no, no, these guys are hard, Tandy.

02:26.880 --> 02:28.709
Not the kind you just roll over.

02:28.710 --> 02:30.019
And yet, that's exactly what happened.

02:32.960 --> 02:34.397
VOICE: [on tape] <i>Everyone, settle.</i>

02:34.460 --> 02:36.079
Okay, who's that?

02:36.080 --> 02:37.879
