going to be a mediator.

02:37.880 --> 02:39.459
Someone both sides trusted.

02:39.460 --> 02:40.668
[high pitched ringing]

02:40.693 --> 02:41.973
EDWIN DUNLAP: [on tape]
<i>Who the hell are you?</i>

02:41.997 --> 02:44.765
[metal clanging, crashing]

02:44.790 --> 02:47.919
- [men grunting, groaning, yelling]
- [glass shatters]

02:47.920 --> 02:49.379
- [metal scraping]
- [man groans]

02:49.404 --> 02:50.517
[tape clicks off]

02:52.460 --> 02:54.674
Ty...

02:54.860 --> 02:56.860
Tyrone, look, I know that this is...

02:58.120 --> 02:59.788
every second that we stay here is

02:59.813 --> 03:01.142
another second we could be
blamed for this.

03:01.166 --> 03:02.736
Tandy, we can't leave.

03:02.761 --> 03:04.960
- We have t...
- What?

03:07.080 --> 03:09.600
I recognize that symbol.

03:09.625 --> 03:12.209
- It's Voudon.
- Voudon as in...

03:12.210 --> 03:13.620
[door opens]

03:15.798 --> 03:17.628
We didn't know who else to call.

03:19.466 --> 03:21.379
I distinctly remember telling you

03:21.380 --> 03:23.579
- to let the police handle this.
- That is what I was doing.

03:23.580 --> 03:25.669
I-I was recording the meeting
so you could have evidence...

03:25.670 --> 03:26.870
BRIGID: You were recording it?

03:26.895 --> 03:29.289
We were the ones that
organized this, Tyrone!

03:29.290 --> 03:30.829
To stop the gang war you started.

03:30.830 --> 03:31.960
That's why I was trying to help.

03:31.991 --> 03:34.249
BRIGID: Oh, yes. Tyrone and his
"helping," I know all about that.

03:34.250 --> 03:36.061
Hey, that's not fair,
he didn't kill anybody...

03:36.085 --> 03:38.239
BRIGID: No, he didn't.
Just like he didn't kill Fuchs?

03:38.264 --> 03:41.079
But it doesn't really matter, does it?
'Cause they're all dead.

03:41.080 --> 03:43.033
