- She was already like that.

34:30.978 --> 34:32.627
I just drive.

34:32.652 --> 34:33.868
- It was a job.
- TANDY: Yeah, well,

34:33.893 --> 34:35.150
I hope that paycheck was worth it.

34:35.152 --> 34:37.322
The other girls, where are they?

34:37.393 --> 34:39.391
[straining, choking] I-I don't know.

34:41.643 --> 34:43.143
PASSENGER: Tomorrow...

34:43.192 --> 34:45.351
