- [chalk breaks]
- [sighs]

35:51.394 --> 35:53.619
[chalk thuds, shatters against wall]

35:54.176 --> 35:55.996
- [sighs]
- EVITA: Don't worry,

35:56.104 --> 35:58.563
it takes most people months
of practice to get it right.

35:58.856 --> 36:00.637
Evita?

36:01.356 --> 36:02.524
What're you doing here?

36:03.934 --> 36:06.498
I came here to apologize.

36:06.591 --> 36:09.143
