when you were opening up to me,

36:15.461 --> 36:17.273
and I was acting
like I knew what it was like

36:17.306 --> 36:19.053
to be in your shoes, and the truth is...

36:19.078 --> 36:20.893
[scoffs]

36:20.894 --> 36:22.524
nobody got kicks like those.

36:24.063 --> 36:27.821
Sometimes they're not great
shoes to be in. Believe me.

36:29.934 --> 36:32.393
