37:37.782 --> 37:39.832
Okay, now, just close your eyes.

37:43.452 --> 37:46.668
Now, take a deep breath.
Just clear your mind.

37:47.590 --> 37:51.710
[Tyrone inhales deeply]

37:54.920 --> 37:57.638
Now, as you draw the veve,

37:57.731 --> 38:00.100
