38:00.163 --> 38:02.793
as if the chalk were your breath,

38:04.300 --> 38:06.469
as if it were your soul.

38:06.470 --> 38:08.800
♪ ♪

38:15.372 --> 38:17.581
Close your eyes.

38:17.918 --> 38:19.680
Breathe.

38:20.340 --> 38:23.919
